{"tid":2194903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊有好多（真）朋友  但永遠都冇打算搵  有幾多人係咁？","createTime":"2020-09-08T22:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T02:50:46.000Z","uid":52520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c73d932d7a003ddbba17467e8ac4adac8eda83ba","tid":2194903,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:09:29.000Z","msg":"（唔想睇自傳  拉落去睇紅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n自己本身有BPD  溝左條女叫好轉左  同時依賴都係傾向左去條女到    有啲症狀好返 有啲就加劇<br />\n<br />\n但幾次既離離合合變到個人開始接受條女係會走  掙扎到就掙扎  <br />\n<br />\n呢加變到你明知有家人  有朋友  但放假冇動力去搵<br />\n連同條女嘈交分手都變到莫名奇妙既平靜   成條死魚訓到係玩手機放一日假就滿足  但又不停loop  <br />\n（我冇朋友？）》（我有朋友）〉（我唔需要朋友）》（係咪我真係冇朋友？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">去到呢到我發覺我係有多一個病  定現今社會發展到大家其實對有朋友都冇咩所謂？</span>"},{"pid":"202cde2617860b8bdd2bf9edd3590e88b46bb397","tid":2194903,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:15:03.000Z","msg":"與其成日覺得自己有邊樣病，不如將佢地當成自己嘅&rdquo;特性&rdquo;啦，有時人地都未標籤你，你就已經先標籤左自己"},{"pid":"a7cfb9f862a152e273ece03c28ae68e44a0ba303","tid":2194903,"uid":360601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:17:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17024be6ff970d9243f56f11ae012590b98be2f7","tid":2194903,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:17:31.000Z","msg":"BPD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 患得患失咁"},{"pid":"344dc335bf3278a2ba02a81fb753deed98d59ab7","tid":2194903,"uid":343268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6814af7df6a45345095def8a36a7f2eb9ca83766","tid":2194903,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T23:23:53.000Z","msg":"人係重覆既痛苦中會學習<br />\n所以第二次失戀慢慢就冇咁痛<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽你描述 你只係冇乜理由/原因去同人接觸<br />\n或者人際關係對你黎講優先程度唔算高<br />\n好聽啲就係享受獨處 難聽就係毒撚格"},{"pid":"c0fb823620bedd9c9ad323aff313b1fa4bbac0ea","tid":2194903,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344dc335bf3278a2ba02a81fb753deed98d59ab7","tid":2194903,"uid":343268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T22:42:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T23:26:10.000Z","msg":"都睇得明嘅"},{"pid":"99638ddd77825cd6705490b9a3fbb514a59068fb","tid":2194903,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:17:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得你欠咗兩個朋友<br />\n一、痴身嘅朋友<br />\n二、會迫你搞活動/約人嘅朋友"},{"pid":"534e6371a7863a369b30ca2561f19b0251bdadbe","tid":2194903,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"廢事俾樓主屌<br />\n加密先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終唔識樓主 所以只係猜測鳩噏<br />\n個人想象力比較豐富<br />\n樓主最簡單 可以話畀我知<br />\n我有幾多%講得啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利：喺手機打字 highlight 打得好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}